{"tid":1479021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來內地平台都開始傳香港的事","createTime":"2019-08-16T17:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T19:03:47.000Z","uid":302183,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc143527d8c43ce5e512c4db808042e6b43722e","tid":1479021,"uid":302183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:36:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟最近用QQ看空間時開始看到在傳什麼我們是搞港獨的。而當我想說並沒有時都是不給我發(這大概是正常吧。<br />\n<br />\n不過在那時，我有朋友說了一個很有趣的提議，就是說幫手宣傳發夢的人可以開個qq然後發個po比人轉發的。(當然開ac發po什麼都要用假ip好)<br />\n<br />\n因為之前有點事件也是這樣宣傳下去。各位覺得怎樣？"},{"pid":"e28c36d3b3197732ae5d8c887b12ed8fce8d31d1","tid":1479021,"uid":54930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"89de724c1a8274eb4692957aec56c6257cd632ba","tid":1479021,"uid":205674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:40:58.000Z","msg":"講乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"a28593370cbf91a0d809ded71ac9df5e2e16402d","tid":1479021,"uid":302183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89de724c1a8274eb4692957aec56c6257cd632ba","tid":1479021,"uid":205674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:40:58.000Z","msg":"講乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n善用不推文回覆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:46:15.000Z","msg":"就係話啱啱同朋友講起如何開個qq號，善用轉發功能當宣傳會不會可行什麼🤔"},{"pid":"9b3fec9e263416e0bf19200f64918f75ca68e782","tid":1479021,"uid":218380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T19:03:47.000Z","msg":"你知唔知自己講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}